\n  print_header() {\n  print_step() {\n  backup_file() {\n  require_confirm() {\n  fix_ssh_config() {\n  fix_firewall() {\n  fix_fail2ban() {\n  fix_low_risk_items() {\n  fix_medium_risk_items() {\n  rollback_backup() {\n  list_backups() {\n  print_report() {\n  show_help() {\n  parse_args() {\n  main() {\n  main \"$@\"\n\n=== cron-manager.sh 核心函数 ===\n  log_info()  { echo -e \"${BLUE}[INFO]${NC}  $1\"; }\n  log_ok()    { echo -e \"${GREEN}[✓]${NC}  $1\"; }\n  log_warn()  { echo -e \"${YELLOW}[⚠]${NC}  $1\"; }\n  log_fail()  { echo -e \"${RED}[✗]${NC}  $1\"; }\n  print_header() {\n  print_step() {\n  check_cron_available() {\n  get_cron_jobs() {\n  get_cron_details() {\n  install_cron_job() {\n  remove_cron_job() {\n  setup_log_rotation() {\n  describe_cron() {\n  next_run_time() {\n  show_cron_help() {\n  send_feishu_notification() {\n  generate_summary_report() {\n  interactive_setup() {\n  show_status() {\n  show_help() {\n  parse_args() {\n  main() {\n  main \"$@\"","cwd":"/workspace/projects/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777109679948},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All 4 scripts are complete and pass syntax checks. Let me provide a summary report.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"All 4 scripts are implemented and pass `bash -n` syntax checks. Here's the summary:\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 实现完成汇报\n\n### 📁 文件清单\n\n| 文件 | 路径 | 行数 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| `quick-detect.sh` | `scripts/quick-detect.sh` | **358行** | ✅ 通过 |\n| `wizard.sh` | `scripts/wizard.sh` | **398行** | ✅ 通过 |\n| `auto-fixer-v2.sh` | `scripts/auto-fixer-v2.sh` | **708行** | ✅ 通过 |\n| `cron-manager.sh` | `scripts/cron-manager.sh` | **740行** | ✅ 通过 |\n\n---\n\n### 1. 🛡️ `quick-detect.sh`（极简模式）\n**核心函数：**\n- `detect_os()` — 检测 Linux 发行版\n- `detect_environment()` — 识别 Docker/VPS/物理机等环境\n- `detect_services()` — 检测 sshd/firewalld/fail2ban 等服务\n- `detect_openclaw()` — 检测 OpenClaw 运行状态和部署模式\n- `quick_security_score()` — 计算 0-100 安全评分\n- `generate_recommendations()` — 生成下一步建议\n- `print_summary()` — 输出带 emoji 的摘要报告\n- `save_report()` — 保存日志到 `~/.openclawhealthcheck/logs/`\n\n**使用：** `bash quick-detect.sh`（无参数，自动检测）\n\n---\n\n### 2. 🎯 `wizard.sh`（中文向导）\n**核心函数：**\n- `step1_machine_type()` — 选择机器类型（个人电脑/VPS/树莓派/公司服务器/Docker）\n- `step2_user_scope()` — 选择使用者范围（仅自己/团队/对外服务）\n- `step3_check_depth()` — 选择检查深度（快速5分钟/标准15分钟/完整30分钟）\n- `show_confirmation()` — 配置确认\n- `execute_checks()` — 根据配置执行相应检查脚本\n- `show_next_steps()` — 检查后提供后续操作选项\n\n**使用：** `bash wizard.sh`（全程交互，无参数）\n\n---\n\n### 3. 🔧 `auto-fixer-v2.sh`（增强版自动修复）\n**核心函数：**\n- `fix_ssh_config()` — 禁用 root 登录 + 密码认证\n- `fix_firewall()` — 启用 ufw 或 firewalld\n- `fix_fail2ban()` — 安装并启动 Fail2ban\n- `fix_low_risk_items()` — standard 模式：SSH 密钥权限/系统更新检查\n- `fix_medium_risk_items()` — high 模式：密码策略/危险服务检查\n- `backup_file()` — 修复前自动备份到 `/root/.healthcheck/backups/`\n- `rollback_backup()` — 按时间戳一键回滚\n- `list_backups()` — 列出所有可用备份\n- `print_report()` — 输出修复统计报告\n\n**使用：**\n```bash\nbash auto-fixer-v2.sh --risk-level safe        # 核心安全\nbash auto-fixer-v2.sh --risk-level standard   # +低风险项\nbash auto-fixer-v2.sh --risk-level high       # +中风险项（需确认）\nbash auto-fixer-v2.sh --rollback --backup=20240101_120000\nbash auto-fixer-v2.sh --list-backups\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. ⏰ `cron-manager.sh`（定时巡检）\n**核心函数：**\n- `check_cron_available()` — 检查 cron 服务状态\n- `install_cron_job()` — 安装定时任务（含表达式验证）\n- `remove_cron_job()` — 删除 OpenClaw 巡检任务\n- `setup_log_rotation()` — 自动配置日志轮转（保留7天）\n- `describe_cron()` / `next_run_time()` — cron 表达式解释\n- `interactive_setup()` — 交互式设置向导\n- `show_status()` — 查看当前巡检状态\n- `send_feishu_notification()` — 飞书通知（待配置 webhook）\n- `generate_summary_report()` — 生成摘要报告\n\n**使用：**\n```bash\nbash cron-manager.sh --cron \"0 2 * * *\"        # 设置每日巡检\nbash cron-manager.sh --cron \"0 */4 * * *\" --notify  # +飞书通知\nbash cron-manager.sh --cron list              # 查看任务\nbash cron-manager.sh --cron remove            # 删除任务\nbash cron-manager.sh --cron status            # 查看状态\nbash cron-manager.sh --cron                   # 交互式设置\n```\n\n---\n\n所有脚本均包含：\n- ✅ `#!/bin/bash` shebang\n- ✅ `# version: 4.9.0-dev` 版本注释\n- ✅ 清晰的函数注释\n- ✅ 中文 + emoji 友好输出\n- ✅ 引入现有的 `backup-functions.sh`"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":769,"output":1086,"cacheRead":69883,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71738,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777109679952,"responseId":"063bbdb0b78ebf0769849282835b3e19"}]}}
